val clicksTemp = sqlContext.read.parquet("/home/ama/sidana/calypso_kk_dec_data/logs/click/es/2016/*/*/")

val usersClickCount = userClicks.groupBy(($"userIdClicks")).count.sort(desc("count"))
z.show(usersClickCount)
